 This version is compiled with g++-3.3, even in the 10.4 tree.  If it is
 ever updated to a more recent compiler, it must be updated at the same time
 as a large collection of packages: fwbuilder, gabber, gabber-ssl, genes, 
 glademm, gnomemm, gtkmm and anything which depends on any of them.
<<
